Resetting Ingredient Values.

This recipe tests whether ingredient values are correctly reset when re-running
a recipe. It should print "2 2 2"

Ingredients.
2 onions

Method.
Serve with Salad.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.
Clean the mixing bowl.
Serve with Salad.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.
Clean the mixing bowl.
Serve with Salad.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.
Refrigerate for 1 hour.

Serves 1.

Salad.

This recipe decrements the value of "peppers".

Ingredients.
3 pepper
1 onion

Method.
Put the pepper into the mixing bowl.
Remove the onion from the mixing bowl.
Fold the pepper into the mixing bowl.
Put the pepper into the mixing bowl.
Refrigerate.
